	(text "Q2 - MMBT3904 Common Emitter\n\nBias divider: R4 = 47kΩ, R5 = 10kΩ\nVbase = 9V × 10k/(47k + 10k) = 1.58V\nVemitter = Vbase - 0.6V = 0.98V\n\nEmitter current:\nIe = Ve / R7 = 0.98V / 1kΩ = 0.98 mA\nIc ≈ Ie = 0.98 mA\n\nCollector voltage:\nVc = 9V - (Ic × R6)\nVc = 9V - (0.98mA × 4.7kΩ) = 4.4V\n\nGain (with C4 bypassing R7):\ngm = Ic / 26mV = 0.98mA / 26mV ≈ 37.7 mS\nAv ≈ gm × R6 = 37.7mS × 4.7kΩ ≈ 177\nAv practical ≈ 40-80 (32-38 dB)\n\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 135.128 160.274 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left top)
		)
		(uuid "0b3870b8-baa8-4ecd-b442-08a196cc916e")
	)
	(text "Not ceramic!"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 105.664 94.234 0)
		(effects
